"```sql\nSELECT COUNT(*) \nFROM account a\nJOIN loan l ON a.account_id = l.account_id\nWHERE l.status IN ('C', 'D') \nAND a.district_id = 1;\n``` \n\nThis SQL query counts the number of accounts that have running contracts (both 'C' for OK and 'D' for client in debt) in the specified branch location (district_id = 1)."